</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_276" id="138r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hansen von Hawsen czum Kunstein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her Hans, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                                                fürgelegt Ulrich Volland und Cristan Crewczer,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, wie ir in etwievil
                                                schuldig bleibt, daz in langczeit von euch
                                                auszengestanden sey, des sie schaden
                                                  <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und nemen über sölch
                                                  <expan>verschreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als euch der
                                                lantfride vormals von iren wegen
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab.
                                                  <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir den
                                                  <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ir schulde noch on
                                                lenger <expan>v<ex>er</ex>czieh<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                                                richten und beczalen und sie darümb unklaghaftig
                                                  <expan>mach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet durch
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>, als etc. Das
                                                  <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>icam</expan>. </ab>
</div>
